Package io.micronaut.views.fields.fetchers

package io.micronaut.views.fields.fetchers
API to fetch elements for option, radio buttons and checkboxes. Used in combination with the InputCheckbox, InputRadio and Select annotations.
Since:
4.1.0
Author:
Sergio del Amo
